| VLAN | Department  | Subnet            | Mask              | Network | First Host | Last Host | Broadcast | Gateway |
|------|-------------|-------------------|------------------|---------|------------|-----------|-----------|---------|
| 10   | Sales       | 192.168.1.0/26    | 255.255.255.192  | .0      | .1         | .62       | .63       | .62     |
| 20   | Engineering | 192.168.1.64/26   | 255.255.255.192  | .64     | .65        | .126      | .127      | .126    |
| 30   | HR          | 192.168.1.128/26  | 255.255.255.192  | .128    | .129       | .190      | .191      | .190    |
| 40   | Service     | 192.168.1.192/26  | 255.255.255.192  | .192    | .193       | .254      | .255      | .254    |

